Rob</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2013 18:16:26 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/1946/nextprev-line-and-page-updown/</guid></item><item><title>Answer by joepd for &lt;p&gt;Hello,
